1. Install django-backup from git@github.com:allanlei/django-backup.git

2. Setup Email settings

    (Example)
    EMAIL_HOST = ''
    EMAIL_HOST_USER = ''
    EMAIL_HOST_PASSWORD = ''
    EMAIL_PORT = 587
    EMAIL_SUBJECT_PREFIX = ''
    EMAIL_USE_TLS = True

3. Run backup command

    Email to abc@abc.com and xyz@abc.com    python manage.py backup_database abc@abc.com xyz@abc.com
    Write to file           python manage.py backup_database --output file
    Outout to stdout        python manage.py backup_database --output stdout
